<section>
<id root="DCCFDFE2-83EE-4F9A-77CB-C8D704BD6533" />
<code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED section" />
<title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml">HOW SUPPLIED</title>
<text><paragraph>Disposable plastic bottles of 220 mL (100 gm of isosorbide/220 mL) for oral use only.</paragraph><paragraph><content styleCode="bold">NDC</content> 0065-0034-08</paragraph><paragraph><content styleCode="bold">Storage:</content> Store at 15&#176;-30&#176;C (59&#176;-86&#176;F).</paragraph><paragraph><content styleCode="bold">CAUTION:</content> Federal ( USA) law prohibits dispensing without prescription.</paragraph><paragraph>Mfd. for<content styleCode="bold">: Alcon Laboratories, Inc.</content></paragraph><paragraph>Fort Worth,  Texas  76134  USA</paragraph><paragraph>Mfd. by: <content styleCode="bold">ALCON (Puerto Rico) INC.</content></paragraph><paragraph>Humacao, Puerto Rico 00791  USA</paragraph><paragraph>July 1997&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Printed in  USA</paragraph><paragraph>249165-0797</paragraph></text>
